<h4>Amazfit X 概念手表今日上架有品众筹，众筹价 999 元</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360687" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06176-01.jpg" alt="" width="6000" height="4000" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06176-01.jpg 6000w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06176-01-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06176-01-768x512.jpg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/DSC06176-01-1024x683.jpg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 6000px) 100vw, 6000px" /></p>
<p>自 2019 年 8 月发布之后，Amazfit X 凭借其「未来式」的外观火了一把。92°曲率 2.07 英寸的 AMOLED 曲面屏、钛金属一体式设计、线性马达和压感按键，取代了传统的实体表冠&#8230; 外观上的别致设计，让这款手表赚足了眼球。</p>
<p>Amazfit X 搭载华米自研的 BioTracker<img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/11/72x72/2122.png" alt="™" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> 2 PPG 可穿戴生物追踪光学传感器，支持心率、血氧、压力、睡眠等健康功能监测。手表支持 7 天超长续航、NFC、运动模式自动识别等功能。</p>
<p>今年 4 月, Amazfit X 在海外的 Indiegogo 平台上开启了众筹, 共有近 12000 多名支持者，众筹资金超过 196 万美元。</p>
<h3><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1293889" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png" alt="" width="1029" height="180" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs.png 1029w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-360x63.png 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-768x134.png 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/12/dagongs-1024x179.png 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1029px) 100vw, 1029px" /></h3>
<h4>微博收购「TS 战队」， 深度布局电竞产业</h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360688" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/WechatIMG38.jpeg" alt="" width="1920" height="1080" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/WechatIMG38.jpeg 1920w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/WechatIMG38-360x203.jpeg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/WechatIMG38-768x432.jpeg 768w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/WechatIMG38-1024x576.jpeg 1024w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px" /></p>
<p>昨天，微博宣布收购 2020 KPL 王者荣耀春季赛和王者荣耀世界冠军杯双料总冠军「豚首王者荣耀战队（TS 战队）」，并将冠军阵容全员保留。此次收购标志着微博正式进军 KPL 领域，深度布局电竞产业。</p>
<p>未来战队将以「WB.TS」为名，继续征战王者荣耀职业联赛（KPL）系列赛事。微博将最大化战队品牌知名度、粉丝基础及俱乐部自身的商业价值，并将搭建完善的青训体系，基于专业化的运营团队更好地支撑俱乐部发展。</p>
<h4><a href="https://weibo.com/6349791448/Jhp0Iacdi?from=page_1006066349791448_profile&amp;wvr=6&amp;mod=weibotime&amp;type=comment#_rnd1598312557779">瑞幸咖啡旗舰店入驻拼多多</a></h4>
<p><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-1360689" src="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/15940177424411.jpg" alt="" width="900" height="600" srcset="https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/15940177424411.jpg 900w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/15940177424411-360x240.jpg 360w, https://s3.ifanr.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/15940177424411-768x512.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px" /></p>
